    "VeroPoint controller with expansion cards",
    "VeroPoint is a standalone and universal programmable controller\n(PLC/DDC) specially designed for monitoring and control purposes\nof heating, ventilation, and cooling systems (HVAC), control systems\nElectricity and energy and closed loop control.\n​\nVeroPoint is the optimal solution for system control and monitoring\nIn public buildings, industry, hospitals, hotels.\n​\nVeroPoint is a standalone controller that includes a battery-backed clock\nThe controller software is stored in non-volatile memory that cannot be deleted.\n​\nThe VeroPoint controller includes a graphical screen that can be programmed as an HMI\nFor convenient and friendly local operation for the purposes of operating schedules and receiving\nreal time data.",
